e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"召天文手足（風向地理問題）<br />\n召出開外景拍攝既手足（電源問題）<br />\n<br />\n[召天文L] 風向對tear gas真係好緊要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e337658dfcafdefe54e4c902abc02ab85d623546","tid":1380242,"uid":171450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31566cd122b545c8447d6dd3060b787ea636fbe4","tid":1380242,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"婆婆..."},{"pid":"dfeafc4a2565beeb394cbda8b1076181511d4114","tid":1380242,"uid":259121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2ba30d451fbaa7095a219cbb67329e8fe64b46","tid":1380242,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"兩隻負皮狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3051eeef5bcfa821aa8278fff8930a149c58d8","tid":1380242,"uid":6528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"001092349419ce313857ab352088d9a741474bc7","tid":1380242,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3051eeef5bcfa821aa8278fff8930a149c58d8","tid":1380242,"uid":6528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"我地係唔會驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a18560b7f6564d4e7a86e4c2178608986e114d0","tid":1380242,"uid":51495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"我地自己知咪得<br />\n咁對婆婆可能係好事<br />\n起碼唔會俾藍絲攻擊"},{"pid":"67c4e03d6d61c18f2843da5880f1df24d08e024f","tid":1380242,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ab99e5514db7dcb2a81077f60c5a36b615ed9","tid":1380242,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13996efc684f9970604c57d3a4c77f650e71c03d","tid":1380242,"uid":202248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"385f687eaa5ef8e5ddb342eddfe7d90bfe5df107","tid":1380242,"uid":171643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"藍絲冇人支持搞到要周圍屈人支持佢地<br />\n陰公 佢地都知自己冇人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5490437fe8a94e52c9571b8a820ceffa34f39be3","tid":1380242,"uid":92385,"like":0,"